fields.name: Lilly's Eco-Clean ALL-PURPOSE SPRAY CLEANER
fields.description: Use for dusting and polishing all your hard surfaces. Lilly’s All Purpose Spray is safe to use around food so it’s an excellent kitchen cleaner that you can use for cleaning cupboards and your fridge. The easy to use microspray bottle gives just right amount of product, not too little, not too much. Lilly’s All Purpose Spray is scientifically proven 99.9% antibacterial
